show.description: Graduate Joyce experiences her boyfriend's infidelity, encounters the cold and stern vampire CEO Herman, who not only is her boss but also the child of her stepfather. Amid misunderstandings and workplace conflicts, the two gradually develop a forbidden love intertwined with betrayal and taboo...
